import React from 'react'
import Head from 'next/head'
import AppLayout from "./components/AppLayouts"

const Singup = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Head>
            <title>회원가입 | NodeBird</title>
        </Head>
        <AppLayouts>회원가입 페이지</AppLayouts>
        </>
    )
}

export default Singup
